Take to the skies with Fly Simulator, a fun and interactive game extension for Chrome that lets you experience the thrill of flying without leaving your desk! Soar through beautifully designed skies, glide over stunning landscapes, and test your piloting skills in various environments.
Perfect for anyone looking for a quick escape or a way to pass the time while learning the basics of flight. Whether you want a relaxing flight or an adrenaline-pumping challenge, Fly Simulator offers endless sky-high fun.
